data.description: Charming 2-large bedroom townhouse, each with its own bath, located near Towne Center Virginia Beach. Situated in a quiet cul-de-sac with a 1-car garage. The kitchen boast custom dark wood cabinets, granite countertops, and stainless steel appliances. Enjoy the Kempsville Lake community amenities like a pool, tennis courts, a clubhouse, and scenic lakes. Proximity to I-264 ensures easy commuting with entertainment all around from trendy restaurants, Lake Trashmore, holiday fireworks and more. Ideal for those seeking comfort and convenience in a fun community.
